features: TrekTote Travel Convenience Kit - Your On-the-Go Companion! Be travel-ready with our compact and TSA-compliant Travel Convenience Kit. Packed with essential travel-size toiletries and accessories, it's perfect for leisure or business trips. Stay fresh and prepared throughout your journey with TrekTote.

Essential Travel-Size Toiletries and Accessories! Travel light with our TrekTote kit. Stay fresh and prepared with grooming and oral care essentials, conveniently packed for your journey. From grooming supplies to oral care necessities, everything you need is within reach.

Designed for Men on the Move! Tailored for men, our kit is versatile for all types of travel. Stay confident on leisure or business trips with TrekTote. It's also a thoughtful gift for Father's Day or any occasion.

Top-Notch National Brand Products Included! Enjoy trusted national brand grooming and hygiene items. Quality products in convenient travel sizes for worry-free travels. Experience the same level of excellence you're accustomed to with full-sized products.

Compact and Convenient! Our TrekTote kit is compact and portable, fitting easily into your carry-on. Travel hassle-free with all your essentials in one place. Say goodbye to packing challenges with our thoughtful convenience kit.
body.description: This all-inclusive 20-piece set includes all these essential items: Bergman and Kelly Shampoo 1 oz: Provides a refreshing and cleansing experience for your hair during your travels. Bergman and Kelly Conditioner 1 oz: Helps nourish and condition your hair, keeping it smooth and manageable on the go. Bergman and Kelly Body Wash: Keeps your body clean and refreshed while on the go. Freshcent Bar Soap: A refreshing bar soap option to cleanse your body during travel or on-the-go. Crest Toothpaste: Maintains a bright smile and fresh breath during your travels. Tanlade Toothbrush: Compact and reliable for dental care on-the-go. Crest Scope Mouthwash 1.2oz: Provides an extra level of oral freshness during your travels. 2 Dental Floss Picks Individually Wrapped: For easy and clean flossing. Twin Blade Razor: Helps keep a clean look. Travelwell Shaving Cream 0.34 oz: A shaving cream that ensures a smooth shave while traveling. Freshcent Deodorant 1.50 oz: A long-lasting deodorant to help you stay fresh and confident throughout the day. McKesson Plastic Comb: A comb to keep your hair looking neat. Two Individual Packet Wipes: Convenient wipes for quick cleaning purposes on-the-go. Two Bandaids: For minor cuts or scrapes that may occur while traveling. Small Pack of Q-tips (Cotton Swabs): Handy cotton swabs for various uses while traveling. Nail Clipper: For maintaining neat and tidy nails during your travels. Advil 2 Tablets: Provides relief for minor aches and pains while on the road. This comprehensive 20-piece set is your ultimate travel companion, ensuring you have all the necessities for a worry-free journey. Stay fresh, confident, and prepared wherever your adventures take you!
